{"tid":1352010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"721 真相！黑警用強光燈同煙霧掩飾開槍射頭！有片！","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:13:43.000Z","uid":227968,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"87ce0a04bc7c13ef4d53498b830c2e4277eeee7c","tid":1352010,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"吹水台重開<br />\n721 真相！<br />\n以下嘅野我都係聽番黎 <br />\n有個人話佢親眼見到 唔知真定假<br />\n因為太多信息 心情未平復 所以而家先打出嚟<br />\n<br />\n警察射催淚彈前係冇衝冇人推<br />\n但有人掟野<br />\n警察持續用超強光射向示威者及記者！<br />\n警察係突然冇舉旗情況下 不斷射催淚彈<br />\nNon stop狂射 好大煙<br />\n然後開始偷雞開槍（分唔出布袋定橡膠）<br />\n因為記者中催淚彈 加上強光 根本影唔到<br />\n有人腳部流血 不斷叫痛 當然太亂<br />\n唔肯定係唔係中槍 啲人圍住又話唔好睇<br />\nfirst aid救救下又射催淚彈 要係咁退<br />\n之後示威者再推 間斷咁聽到啲盾同金屬板中彈嘅聲音<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成個過程就係 放你催淚 射你強光 再偷雞開你槍</span><br />\n<br />\n另外有線影到催淚彈射中頭，不過盾擋左（1:32）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1163236017201798?s=1125494791&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1163236017201798%3Fs%3D1125494791%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=843a6231\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1163236017201798?s=1125494791&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79p61uF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79p61uF.png&h=50b61128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上環用強光同煙霧掩飾開槍<br />\n元朗出黑社會打人<br />\n兩樣同樣重要<br />\n8點話清場 好後嘅人開始散<br />\n10點幾就出黑社會去北區打人<br />\n冇夾過邊個信<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n轉自長川谷先生"},{"pid":"9983c10dc687fb3af4b75edf5fa447e048444d08","tid":1352010,"uid":269616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:13:56.000Z","msg":"福佳黑警"},{"pid":"88c6d54e119ff25ef9b9f8eaf7e67bb3c62abc97","tid":1352010,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:10:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60df2e882de5dc9d2f93a80a2eadf4da84725acb","tid":1352010,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:06:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3ccda604370ce90905597c5f9bfe07263f0a351","tid":1352010,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efcb0f781ebeb4cb57918c8c94cfe76da39badad","tid":1352010,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bf8da41138491227d6910dc28cfea78ee637e81","tid":1352010,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2153dac1204511f39527a34cef41e5af5b78e781","tid":1352010,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}